Package: sitemix
Title: Site- and Group-Level Proportions, Rates, and Sampling Uncertainty
Version: 0.2.0
Date: 2026-07-12
Authors@R: c(
    person("JoonHo", "Lee", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "jlee296@ua.edu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0006-4019-8703"))
  )
Description: Computes year-by-year site-level point estimates and asymptotic standard
    errors of proportions and rates for three families: 'binomial' for single binary
    indicators, 'multivariate' for overlapping binary indicators with joint counts
    and seemingly unrelated regression covariance, and 'multinomial' for mutually
    exclusive categories with full-simplex covariance. Accepts either student-level
    rows or sufficient-count rows as input and returns a 'sitemix_estimates' tibble
    with an optional variance-covariance list-column for downstream uncertainty
    propagation. Also accepts published aggregate rows through the D0
    aggregate-binomial path and the D1 aggregate-marginal working-independence path.
URL: https://joonho112.github.io/sitemix/,
    https://github.com/joonho112/sitemix
